{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Death Scourges is a linear and dark third person shooter mixed with tactical elements. You embody the captain of a special strike team consisting of four elite operators. Shoot, loot, craft and use your team to survive the unknown horror lurking in the depths of an underground research facility.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">SHED LIGHT INTO THE DARK</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2198250/extras/start2.gif?t=1736264620\" />You're send to a mysterious underground facility and have to investigate a leak from one of your contact persons. The deeper you descend, the more truth unveils...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">THIRD PERSON COMBAT</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2198250/extras/combat2.gif?t=1736264620\" />Target your enemies with the classic over-the-shoulder perspective.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">THE TEAM IS YOUR WEAPON</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2198250/extras/team2.gif?t=1736264620\" />Giving your teammates efficient orders will increase your chances of survival.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">WEAPON ARSENAL</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2198250/extras/craft2.gif?t=1736264620\" />Make use of pistols, SMGs, shotguns, assault rifles, snipers and special weapons such as a flamethrower and even more.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">CRAFTING</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_